@startuml
skinparam BackgroundColor white
node "Client Machine" {
    artifact "redis-benchmark" as RedisBench
}

node "Server Machine (Linux)" {
    node "Kernel Space" {
        component "TCP/IP Stack" as TCP
        component "epoll instance" as EpollK
    }
    node "User Space (Single Core)" {
        component "Cache Server Process" as CacheServer {
            component "Reactor Loop" as Reactor
            database "In-Memory Hash Table" as HT
        }
    }
}

RedisBench <--> TCP : Network (Loopback/LAN)
TCP <--> EpollK : Kernel Buffers
EpollK <--> Reactor : System Calls (epoll_wait, read, write)
Reactor --> HT : In-Memory Operations
@enduml
